<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.4.8">
<l>kaṉṟiṉai vālōlai kaṭṭik kaṉika ḷutira veṟintu</l>
<l>piṉṟoṭarn tōṭiyōr pāmpaip piṭittukkoṇ ṭāṭṭiṉāy pōlum</l>
<l>niṉṟiṟat tēṉallēṉ nampi nīpiṟan tatiru naṉṉāḷ</l>
<l>naṉṟunīnīrāṭa vēṇṭum nārāṇā vōṭātē vārāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It seems, having tied palm leaves to the tail of a calf</l>
<l>and throwing [it] so that ripe fruits dropped [down],</l>
<l>you went running after a snake, and having caught [it],</l>
<l>danced [upon it’s head].</l>
<l>Nampi, I do not have your strength.</l>
<l>[This] is the sacred day upon which you were born.</l>
<l>You must bathe well in water, Nārāṇā!</l>
<l>Come [here], do not run away!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
